dcterms:description: The DAIC-WOZ dataset contains clinical interviews designed to support the diagnosis of psychological distress conditions such as anxiety, depression, and post-traumatic stress disorder. It includes audio and video recordings, and extensive questionnaire responses from interviews conducted by an animated virtual interviewer controlled by a human interviewer.
dcterms:title: Distress Analysis Interview Corpus - a Wizard of Oz (DAIC-WOZ)
